# README
## Create config/secret.js file
`
export const seedphases = [
    {
        name: "wave-wallet-1",
        seedphase: "..."
    }
]
`

## Generate multiple private key from seedphases
```
node generate.js
```

## Steps to run
```
node send-gas.js
node collect-ocean.js
node collect-sui.js
node swap-ocean-sui.js
node check-balance.js
```
